Constructor Detail

CAnalyzer.Specifiers

public CAnalyzer.Specifiers(GNode specifiers,
                            boolean refIsDecl)
Create a new sequence of specifiers. This constructor analyzes the specified AST node and may print error messages as a result.

Parameters:
specifiers - The node holding the declaration specifiers (which may be null).
refIsDecl - The flag for whether a struct/union reference also is a struct/union declaration.
